  <section class="w-full py-12 lg:py-24 xl:py-32">
    <div
      class="px-4 md:px-12 mx-auto max-w-7xl py-12 lg:px-32 flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12 lg:gap-16"
    >
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <div
            class="inline-block rounded-lg bg-[var(--clr-tags)] px-3 py-1 text-sm text-[var(--clr-base-text)]"
          >
            About Us
          </div>
          <h1 class="text-3xl font-black sm:text-5xl text-[var(--clr-h-text)]">
            We're on a mission to help create social media.
          </h1>
        </div>
        <p
          class="max-w-[900px] text-[var(--clr-base-text)] md:text-xl/relaxed lg:text-base/relaxed xl:text-xl/relaxed"
        >
          Our journey began with a simple idea: to create something meaningful.
          We've always believed in the power of innovation and the impact it can
          have on the world. That's why we've dedicated ourselves to pushing the
          boundaries of what's possible.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid items-start gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
          <p class="text-[var(--clr-base-text)]">
            We're driven by a desire to make a difference, to leave the world a
            little better than we found it. Whether it's through our work, our
            community, or our commitment to sustainability, we believe that
            every action has the power to create positive change.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--clr-base-text)]">
            At our core, we're dreamers and doers, thinkers and tinkerers. We're
            not afraid to take risks, to challenge the status quo, to imagine
            the impossible. And we're always looking for others who share our
            passion, who want to join us on this adventure, who believe that
            together, we can change the world.
